{"TopicId":181558,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"Do y\u0026#039;all think the Space-X Super heavy/Star ship would work out?","CreatedByName":"Cloakedwand72","CreatedById":38144,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-20T23:08:20Z","PageNum":11,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-10T11:18:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey may\u00A0revive the old idea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022mercury-space-station.gif?w=584\u0026amp;h=357\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022358\u0022 src=\u0022https://falsesteps.files.wordpress.com/2012/11/mercury-space-station.gif?w=584\u0026amp;h=357\u0022 width=\u0022584\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Then we need Infernal Robotics to mod)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-02-10T11:20:06Z\u0022 title=\u002202/10/2019 11:20  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 10, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-10T11:46:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223538047\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022181558\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221549797488\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188222\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xd the great\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 minutes ago, Xd the great said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs someone suggesting to add a fully functional dragon v2 into a cargo starship?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEvidently. It has all the required functionality, and enough crew capacity for early missions to Moon and Mars. A Mars mission will likely eat up the rest of the cargo space with habitat equipment.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr... or... we could create a vertical stack of several Dragons!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223538048\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022181558\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221549797504\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey may\u00A0revive the old idea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s unnecessary due to vehicle configuration and width.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, I love the look of a crew transfer tunnel blister.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-10T11:55:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223538058\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022181558\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221549799209\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146349\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DDE\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, DDE said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEvidently. It has all the required functionality, and enough crew capacity for early missions to Moon and Mars. A Mars mission will likely eat up the rest of the cargo space with habitat equipment.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr... or... we could create a vertical stack of several Dragons!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter landing the rockets on a \u003Cs\u003Ebarge\u003C/s\u003E ADS, a ship with a trampoline net, and a 1950s style steel rocket, we hardly can get to wonder...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xd the great","CreatedById":188222,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-10T12:58:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223538058\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022181558\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221549799209\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146349\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DDE\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, DDE said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr... or... we could create a vertical stack of several Dragons!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNASA continues screaming in agony\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nImagine starship releasing 3 dragon capsules to dock with the ISS.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Dragon 1 Big Brother has been released from the ISS, Dragon 2 Big Brother commencing docking procedure.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-10T13:19:55Z","Content":"